parameters:
The customers seem to have taken a liking to it
all at once.

Black-suited person: This is how it is during this
time. Please take the customers' orders and relay
them to the kitchen.

Customer A: Um, one draft beer and one highball,
and also fried chicken and french fries.

Customer B: Hmm... do you have any
recommendations?
Well... how about trying our special sausages?

Customer B: .... What's the difference between
that and regular sausages?

Our sausages at this establishment are longer,
thicker, and have a rich flavor compared to those
sold in stores.

Customer B: Hmm... so you like sausages, huh? How
do you usually eat them?

I actually love them piping hot♡ So I'll just pop
a freshly made one into my mouth and savor it all
at once♪

Customer B: Oh... so do you also take cocks all at
once?
Well, when it comes to penises...

Customer B: Well then, shall I get one of your
favorite special 'sausages', big sister? *smirks*

Customer C: Oh, you have a nice body, employee-
san ♡ I'll take you out for some 'delivery'.
Gahaha!

Customer D: Hey hey, cut it out with those jokes.
Sorry about that, my friend said something weird.
Well then, may I take your order...

Customer D: Hmm, in that case, I'll have a Jim
Lock cocktail, plum wine with hot water, and
sautéed beef skirt steak...
Customer D: Can I have one of these big peaches?

Ayako, who continued to be harassed by drunken
customers, took their orders...

Black Suit: Good job. It's amazing that you were
able to move that much on your first day.
....Are the customers here always like this...?

Black Suit: Given the location, there are indeed
many customers like that.

Black Suit: If you'd like, would you prefer to be
assigned to the stage?

(If I have to endure being touched on the butt,
maybe it would be better for me to be assigned to
the stage... Should I ask for that?)
I'm sorry, but please let me do that...

Black Suit: Understood. However, we can't change
the assignments too often, so please stay assigned
to the stage for a while.

Yes, I understand. By the way, when will the
membership card be issued?

Black Suit: It will be ready soon, so it looks
like we can hand it over by the time the next job
is finished.

(Alright... It looks like I can enter that room
now... I wonder what kind of room it is...?)

(But... next is assisting with the show, huh...
Maybe I should try practicing some magic or
something)

Ayako, who had her position changed from the hall
to avoid being sexually harassed by a customer...

However, Ayako couldn't imagine the content of the
show that would be held in this shop...! After
returning home, Ayako leisurely practiced magic
tricks...
The lewdness level has increased by 2...

Ayako earned 5000 yen as her part-time job
payment.
